# Simple Java REST API

## How to run locally

1. Compile  
   javac ItemApiServer.java

2. Run  
   java ItemApiServer

Server starts at: http://localhost:8000

## API Endpoints

POST /items  
- Add new item  -
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post `
-Uri "http://localhost:8000/items" `
-ContentType "application/json" `
-Body '{"name":"Phone","description":"Samsung"}'


GET /items/{id}  
- Get item by ID
Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri "http://localhost:8000/items/ID"

